{
    "version": "3",
    "description": "Offline command line lookup utility for GTFOBins.",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/nccgroup/GTFOBLookup",
    "license": "GPL-3.0",
    "suggest": {
        "python": "uv"
    },
    "url": "https://github.com/nccgroup/GTFOBLookup/archive/refs/tags/v3.zip",
    "hash": "e5846b55c11d3e5e54dd7015c8f0f420a01fb1a248d93c732c046a36dedc0a48",
    "pre_install": [
        "Set-Content \"$dir\\GTFOBLookup.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0",
        "@uv run python \"gtfoblookup.py\" %*",
        "@popd' -Encoding Ascii"
    ],
    "post_install": [
        "Move-Item -Path \"$dir\\GTFOBLookup-$version\\*\" -Destination \"$dir\\\"",
        "Remove-Item \"$dir\\GTFOBLookup-$version\" -Force -Recurse",
        "uv venv \"$dir\\.venv\"",
        "uv pip install -r $dir\\requirements.txt --python \"$dir\\.venv\\Scripts\\python.exe\""
    ],
    "bin": "GTFOBLookup.bat",
    "checkver": "github",
    "autoupdate": {
        "url": "https://github.com/nccgroup/GTFOBLookup/archive/refs/tags/v$version.zip"
    },
    "notes": [
        "【工具类型】: Python工具",
        "【主要功能】: Offline command line lookup utility for GTFOBins.",
        "【适用场景】: 权限提升信息查询、安全测试、CTF竞赛",
        "【技术特点】: 基于Python开发，需Python环境"
    ]
}
